Subject: drm/i915: Extract pipe_mbus_dbox_ctl()
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 45bc523009f0c289b0f1354de007f3c61958e8c0
